  "screens": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "好。",
        "现在假设你真的想做一个交易系统。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "你最先缺的，",
        "往往不是策略灵感。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "而是 **<term id=\"data\">数据</term>**。",
        "有个比喻很贴切：算法像车，数据像燃料。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "data"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "data"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "车再好，没油也跑不起来。",
        "算法也是一样。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "而且数据不是“拿来就用”。",
        "它先要被收集。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "**<term id=\"data_collection\">数据收集</term>** 很花时间。",
        "找源头、拿权限、清洗格式，都会卡人。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "data_collection"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "data_collection"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "接着是 **<term id=\"data_storage\">数据存储</term>**。",
        "因为数据量会很大，而且类型不只数字。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "data_storage"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "data_storage"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "文本、图片、音频、视频，",
        "都可能变成交易系统的输入。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "然后是 **<term id=\"data_management\">数据管理</term>**。",
        "格式不一致时，传统数据库也会开始吃力。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "data_management"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "data_management"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "type": "exercise",
      "lines": [
        "先别急着想模型。",
        "你觉得哪个环节最像“把油搬进油箱”？"
      ],
      "exercise": {
        "kind": "single_choice",
        "prompt": "选一个最贴近数据基础工作的答案。",
        "options": [
          "数据收集与清洗",
          "凭感觉调参数",
          "盯盘等灵感"
        ],
        "answer": 0,
        "explanation": "材料把数据看成燃料，前面这些基础活就是在让系统有油可用。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "还有 **<term id=\"data_processing\">数据处理</term>**。",
        "重点不是能不能处理，而是处理得够不够快、够不够稳。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "data_processing"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "data_processing"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "再往下，问题就不再只是数据了。",
        "而是整套基础设施。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "现实里会冒出很多部件：",
        "实时行情、历史数据、硬件、券商连接、网络延迟。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "还有 **<term id=\"oms\">订单管理系统</term>**、",
        "算法维护和网络安全。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "oms"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "oms"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "type": "exercise",
      "lines": [
        "看到这里，",
        "你应该已经感觉到一件事。"
      ],
      "exercise": {
        "kind": "single_choice",
        "prompt": "做交易系统更像下面哪一个？",
        "options": [
          "只写一段买卖逻辑",
          "搭一整套数据与执行流水线",
          "只要会看 K 线就够了"
        ],
        "answer": 1,
        "explanation": "材料反复强调真实世界里需要数据、连接、系统与维护。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "顺着这个视角，",
        "常见的交易方法还能继续往下分。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "**<term id=\"fundamental_analysis\">基本面分析</term>** 看基本面。",
        "比如公司、行业、财务和管理层。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "fundamental_analysis"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "fundamental_analysis"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "**<term id=\"technical_analysis\">技术分析</term>** 看图形与趋势。",
        "它盯的是价格行为。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "technical_analysis"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "technical_analysis"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "**<term id=\"quantitative_analysis\">量化分析</term>** 更强调规则、统计和模型。",
        "包括 <term id=\"rule_based\">规则策略</term>、套利、<term id=\"nlp\">自然语言处理</term> 和 <term id=\"machine_learning\">机器学习</term>。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "quantitative_analysis",
        "rule_based",
        "nlp",
        "machine_learning"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "quantitative_analysis",
        "rule_based",
        "nlp",
        "machine_learning"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "还有按时间来分。",
        "<term id=\"long_term\">长期</term>、<term id=\"short_term\">中短期</term>、<term id=\"intraday\">日内</term>、<term id=\"high_frequency\">高频</term>。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "long_term",
        "short_term",
        "intraday",
        "high_frequency"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "long_term",
        "short_term",
        "intraday",
        "high_frequency"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "时间越短，",
        "对速度、连接和执行细节通常越敏感。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "把这句 punchline 带走就够了：",
        "做交易系统，先别只盯策略，先看你有没有系统。"
      ]
    }
